                c.conname, c.confrelid, array_to_string(c.conkey, ',', '*') as conkey_string,
                c.conrelid
          FROM pg_catalog.pg_constraint c) c
   ON c.conrelid = cl.oid
  JOIN pg_catalog.pg_attribute a
   ON  c.unnest_conkey = a.attnum

  ON c.confrelid = tns.oid
 WHERE NOT a.attisdropped
   AND cl.relname = 'Extract'

SELECT "t0"."Calculation_7540328115524419" AS "Calculation_7540328115524419",
  "t0"."College" AS "College",
  "t0"."avg:Math:ok" AS "avg:Math:ok",
  "t0"."avg:Verbal:ok" AS "avg:Verbal:ok",
  "t0"."avg:Writing:ok" AS "avg:Writing:ok",
  "t0"."sum:Calculation_4404168645794844673:ok" AS "sum:Calculation_4404168645794844673:ok",
  "t1"."$temp1_output" AS "sum:Calculation_554505731386286080:ok"
FROM (
  SELECT (("Extract"."Math" + "Extract"."Verbal") + "Extract"."Writing") AS "Calculation_7540328115524419",
    "Extract"."College" AS "College",
    AVG(CAST("Extract"."Math" AS DOUBLE PRECISION OR NULL)) AS "avg:Math:ok",
    AVG(CAST("Extract"."Verbal" AS DOUBLE PRECISION OR NULL)) AS "avg:Verbal:ok",
    AVG(CAST("Extract"."Writing" AS DOUBLE PRECISION OR NULL)) AS "avg:Writing:ok",
    SUM(1) AS "sum:Calculation_4404168645794844673:ok"
  FROM "Extract"."Extract" "Extract"
  GROUP BY 1,
    2
) "t0"
  CROSS JOIN (
  SELECT (CAST(SUM((("Extract"."Math" + "Extract"."Verbal") + "Extract"."Writing")) AS DOUBLE PRECISION OR NULL) / NULLIF(SUM(1),0)) AS "$temp1_output"
  FROM "Extract"."Extract" "Extract"
  HAVING (COUNT(1) > 0)
) "t1"

       d.description

SELECT c.contype, c.conname, a.attname, a.attnotnull, tns.relname, unnest_conkey, conkey_string, tns.nspname as ref_ns
  FROM pg_catalog.pg_class cl
  JOIN ( SELECT c.contype, unnest(c.conkey) AS unnest_conkey,
                c.conname, c.confrelid, array_to_string(c.conkey, ',', '*') as conkey_string,
                c.conrelid
          FROM pg_catalog.pg_constraint c) c
   ON c.conrelid = cl.oid
  JOIN pg_catalog.pg_attribute a
   ON  c.unnest_conkey = a.attnum
   AND a.attrelid      = cl.oid
  LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t.oid, t.relname, ns.nspname
    FROM pg_catalog.pg_class t
    JOIN pg_catalog.pg_namespace ns
      ON ns.oid = t.relnamespace
    WHERE t.relkind IN('r','v','f')
     AND ns.nspname not like 'pg_catalog') tns
  ON c.confrelid = tns.oid

FROM "Extract"."Extract" "Extract"
WHERE (("Extract"."City" >= 'Aberdeen') AND ("Extract"."City" <= 'Yuma') AND ("Extract"."Order Date" >= (DATE '2014-01-03')) AND ("Extract"."Order Date" <= (DATE '2017-10-31')))
GROUP BY 1

SELECT "Extract"."City" AS "City"
FROM "Extract"."Extract" "Extract"
WHERE (("Extract"."City" >= 'Aberdeen') AND ("Extract"."City" <= 'Yuma'))
GROUP BY 1
